{
  "texts": [
    "Transformers have been shown to outperform the previous architectural paradigm used in this domain (Dai et al., 2021).",
    "Moreover, when transformers are considered in the medical field, it is for their capacity to accept different modalities of data (He et al., 2023).",
    "This quality is attractive in healthcare, where multi-modal data is increasingly more available (Acosta et al., 2022).",
    "Therefore, we must judge transformers' abductive reasoning capability in different modalities.",
    "The abductive reasoning capacity of transformers has been most explored in NLP (Bhagavatula et al., 2020)."
  ]
}